servlets.util

Class MiniStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • servlets.util.MiniStatus

  • public class MiniStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    The class stores only some of the details provided by a Twitter 4j status. This allows statuses to be easily returned from the storage.
    Author:
    tudorsirbu
